{"tid":1127230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國經濟穩定了？首季就業狀況4年最差","createTime":"2019-04-27T03:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T18:39:19.000Z","uid":54733,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e33da6949bc892e036cf1f898bc9d3a0923dbfa9","tid":1127230,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190426/bkn-20190426200943039-0426_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190426%2Fbkn-20190426200943039-0426_00842_001.html&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcswQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=01896931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190426/bkn-20190426200943039-0426_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190426/photo/bkn-20190426200943039-0426_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190426203442\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190426%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190426200943039-0426_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190426203442&h=b4c6a12a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(美聯社圖片)<br />\n<br />\n外國傳媒報道，中國今年首3個月經濟增長達6.4%，好過市場預期，但勞工市場狀況則為2015年以來最差，主因是企業對工人的需求減少，以及待業人士數量驟增。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://網上求職網站Zhaopin.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%B1%82%E8%81%B7%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99Zhaopin.com&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcswQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=cd35bae8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">網上求職網站Zhaopin.com</a>發布的數據顯示，今年首3個月中國職位空缺與求職者的比例跌至1.68，大幅低於去年第4季的2.38及去年首季的1.91，為2015年初有紀錄以來最低。與去年第4季相比，職位空缺大跌7.6%，而求職人數則大升31%。<br />\n<br />\n以行業劃分的話，科技行業招聘量已由首位大跌至第5位，中介服務、教育、藥品，以及保險行業則分別排名首四位。<br />\n<br />\n更甚的是，目前若想在中國大城市工作，職位已「爭崩頭」，大約每兩名工人爭奪一個職位，即每份工作與每名工人的比例約0.51，較去年首季的0.71大幅下跌。Zhaopin更預期，最差的情況仍未出現，今年次季求職市場恐更趨緊張。"},{"pid":"caa4f72c214f4560436916a6224e872ad531c883","tid":1127230,"uid":40470,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n失業後生女來香港"},{"pid":"595b153f6c04361460f75216335c4193c1ba0e14","tid":1127230,"uid":54733,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:12:02.000Z","msg":"大城市都搵唔到野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2528c7808768a218e0c9395631c76b2a791627d","tid":1127230,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:16:56.000Z","msg":"產能過剩<br />\nAI代替重復工作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 解決唔到失業果班無救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da24a6893fcde7910c627ef18d950d469c7e84de","tid":1127230,"uid":201926,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:21:39.000Z","msg":"咩呀，富起來個個劈炮出黎創業咋，好似係"},{"pid":"004b6e43e45feed2796e3de1243f4735d360febe","tid":1127230,"uid":145277,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"同場加映美國gdp<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://www.hk01.com/%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A/322552/%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25AD%25A3gdp%25E5%25A2%259E%25E9%2595%25B73-2-%25E9%2581%25A0%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%25A0%2590%25E6%259C%259F&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjBp5TlqO_hAhWCFogKHckYAjoQxfQBMAF6BAgIEAg&amp;usg=AOvVaw0HCcqxCZUx9qytxxXqN9H5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%2525E8%2525B2%2525A1%2525E7%2525B6%252593%2525E5%2525BF%2525AB%2525E8%2525A8%25258A%2F322552%2F%2525E7%2525BE%25258E%2525E5%25259C%25258B%2525E9%2525A6%252596%2525E5%2525AD%2525A3gdp%2525E5%2525A2%25259E%2525E9%252595%2525B73-2-%2525E9%252581%2525A0%2525E5%25258B%25259D%2525E5%2525B8%252582%2525